arStrings.szText: Captain Kharov banished me for what I wrote. You are my way back into his good graces!
Perhaps you can do whatever Kharov needs. As his Scribe, I've seen his ups and downs, and I know he hungers for an equal. Someone worthy of his respect.
Your success in the Blood Pilgrimage will be proof of such! Collect the Condemned Trophy and make your way through the temple streets. Do as Kharov once did!
